Use this command to check for feedback, responses, or comments on Linear issues. Perfect for seeing if your questions have been answered or if there are new comments requiring your attention.

Perfect for:
- Checking if feedback request has been answered
- Reviewing responses to your questions
- Seeing new comments from teammates
- Following up on blocked issues
- Daily check for updates on active issues

